    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "description",
      "label": "Description",
      "default": "<p>India's first winter jacket for medicos – made for warmth, movement, and focus. Fleece-bonded fabric, stretch back panels, and functional pockets for everything your shift demands. Built for layering over scrubs.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_text",
      "label": "Button text",
      "default": "Shop Now"
    },
    {
